    section#section_summary
      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-md-5
          h2 Qick Summary
        .summary.col-xs-12.col-md-6
          ul
            li The first javascript framework of Vue.js I used in website developement.
            li The first seven works were completed by following <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCHX_XMhPrtvOmgGOnA2eTmA" target="_blank">a live coding on YouTube</a>.
            li Understanding the differce between Vue.js and other front-end framework, such as Angular.js or React.js.
            li I have learned how to use Vue.js and when to use component object.
    hr
    section#section_detail
      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-md-12
          h2 Features
      .row.detail_row
        .col-xs-12.col-md-6
          .outer_container
            .display(style="background-image: url('../image/vue-starter-project/feature-hotel.png');")
            h3 Hotel Management Page
        .col-xs-12.col-md-6
          .text
            p Management page with hotel information
            ul
              li The website was based on the feature of two-way data binding.
              li Understanding the component and its attributes with vue instance.
              li Basic UI design with bootstrap.
            a(href="https://yrfang.github.io/Vue.js-projects/02%20-%20hotel-management/index.html" target="blank") View More
      .row.detail_row
        .col-xs-12.col-md-6
          .outer_container
            .display(style="background-image: url('../image/vue-starter-project/feature-1-slideshow.png');")
            h3 Vue.js Slideshow
        .col-xs-12.col-md-6
          .text
            p Vue.js photo slideshow
            ul
              li Breif UI design with interesting slogan.
              li Much familiar with Vue.js features.
            a(href="https://yrfang.github.io/Vue.js-projects/04%20-%20slogan-slideshow/index.html" target="_blank") View More
      .row.detail_row
        .col-xs-12.col-md-6
          .outer_container
            .display(style="background-image: url('../image/vue-starter-project/feature-3-switchable-table.png');")
            h3 Switchable Table
        .col-xs-12.col-md-6
          .text
            p Switchable table with big and small grid view
            ul
              li A good excercise for if/esle condition practice in Vue.js framework.
            a(href="https://yrfang.github.io/Vue.js-projects/08%20-%20swtichable-grid/index.html" target="_blank") View More
      .row.detail_row
        .col-xs-12.col-md-6
          .outer_container
            .display(style="background-image: url('../image/vue-starter-project/feature5-simple-search.png');")
            h3 Vue.js Table
        .col-xs-12.col-md-6
          .text
            p Searchable table for country's dial code
            ul
              li Data in table was available with JQuery AJAX.
              li I have realized "filter function" of JS and used it to implement the keyword search.
              li I also used arrow function of ES6 in the work to achieve more breif codes.
            a(href="https://yrfang.github.io/Vue.js-projects/07%20-%20dial-code-search/index.html" target="_blank") View More
